Name: ATP-energy
Comment: virtual/abstract metabolite, exchange of ATP against ADP and Pi

Name: NADH-redox-potential
Comment: virtual/abstract metabolite, exchange of NADH against NAD

Name: NADPH-redox-potential
Comment: virtual/abstract metabolite, exchange of NADPH against NADP

Name: FADH-redox-potential
Comment: virtual/abstract metabolite, exchange of FADH2 against FAD

Name: Proton-gradient
Comment: virtual/abstract metabolite, exchange of a proton across a membrane

Name: activated-sulphur
Comment: virtual/abstract metabolite, exchange of PAPS against PAP

Name: Adenosylmethioninamine-potential
Comment: virtual/abstract metabolite exchange of C01137 against C00170

Name: Glycogenin
Comment: This compound refers to the unglycosylated peptide.

Name: Glycogenin-G11
Comment: Autocatalytically glycosylated glycogenin plus additonal 1-4 glucose residues attached by glycogen synthase.

Name: Glycogenin-G4G7
Comment: Represents the result of the activity of the glycogen branching enzyme.

Name: Glycogenin-G4G4
Comment: phosphorylase-limit-dextrin, i.e. glycogen after the cleavage of 1-4 glucose bonds by glycogen phosphorylase

Name: Glycogenin-G7G1
Comment: Represents the product of the debranching activity of the glycogen debranching enzyme.

Name: Glycogenin-G7
Comment: Glycogenin with 7 (1-4) glucose residues. Represents the product of the glycogen debranching enzyme.
